# TC42 : ObstacleDetectedBoost9
# Related normal-mode case : TC32_ObstacleDetected9
# Precondition : BoostMode, forward=false
# Action : left + right obstacle detected, front clear
# Expected : BoostMode 유지, CleanerDriver mode=boost 유지, no change from backward escape state
power
start
dust
expect mode BoostMode
expect cleaner on
expect cleanerMode boost
obstacle 1 1 1
expect mode BoostMode
expect cleanerMode boost
expect motorForward false
obstacle 0 1 1
expect mode BoostMode
expect cleaner on
expect cleanerMode boost
expect motor moving
expect motorForward false
exit
